Metadata: Ocean and Coastal Law Memo (Issue 39, March 1983)
Oregon State University Extension/Sea Grant Program

Ocean and Coastal Law Memo is an aperiodic publication of the University of Oregon Ocean and Coastal Law Center (OCLC) and is distributed by the Oregon State University Extension/Sea Grant Program. The following topic is in this issue: Recent Developments in Ocean and Coastal Law, 1992, M. Brown and B. Shavelson.
